title: A Prison Wedding with Ti Ti Jerry | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 72
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
Sally babes is out this week so Chris is joined by Ti Ti Jerry! If you don't know who Ti Ti Jerry is then STRAP IN!!!! We learn about how her wedding went in prison. She got married multiple times! PRISON FLINGS ARE HOT!!! The merch is out now babes!!! Check it out on the store tab of Sals Website - salvulcanocomedy.com
